Installation:

To untar the file, type:
	tar -xvzf Chess_V1.0_src.tar.gz
Navigate to the chess directory:
	cd chess
Install the program:
	make
To run the program, navigate to the bin directory and run chess:
	cd bin
	./chess
To uninstall the program:
	make clean

More detailed instructions on the installation/uninstallation of this program can be found in the
software specification manual.
